query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(cn mc) NoMergeJoin(cn mc ct) NoMergeJoin(cn ct mc t mk) NoMergeJoin(cn ct mc mk t k) NoMergeJoin(cn ct k mc mk t ml) NoMergeJoin(cn ct k mc mk ml t lt) */ select min(cn.name) AS from_company,
min(mc.note) AS production_note,
min(t.title) AS movie_based_on_book
from company_name AS cn
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on mc.company_id = cn.id AND cn.country_code <> '[pl]' AND mc.note IS NOT NULL
inner join company_type AS ct
on mc.company_type_id = ct.id AND ct.kind IS NOT NULL AND ct.kind <> 'production companies'
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 1994
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on t.id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
inner join keyword AS k
on mk.keyword_id = k.id AND k.keyword IN ('tv-special',
'murder-in-title',
'superhero')
inner join movie_link AS ml
on ml.movie_id = t.id AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mk.movie_id
inner join link_type AS lt
on lt.id = ml.link_type_id;
